This file has the devops best practices when syncing dev -> prod

Step 1: As usual, you will commit and push the changes from dev -> dev repo. After follow the below steps,

# Pull latest Prod code (to ensure no drift)

git fetch martechanalyticsprod

# Compare

git diff martechanalyticsprod/master --stat

# Dev -> Prod

git push martechanalyticsprod master

# Verify

git fetch --all
git diff martechanalyticsdev/master martechanalyticsprod/master --stat

# Best Practice

After each successful promotion, tag the release:

git tag -a v1.0.1 -m "Promoted stable Google Ads pipeline to Prod"
git push martechanalyticsprod v1.0.1

